title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 135: Featuring Cam Janssen
description:
On Thursday's episode of Spittin' Chiclets, the guys are joined by former NHL enforcer and current talk show host Cam Janssen. Cam joins to talk about some funny stories, his role as an enforcer, some ups and downs in his life and a ton more. The guys also touch on Tom Wilson's big TKO, Biz getting snubbed by Call Her Daddy, Carter Hart and more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
